<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= lab.title %> — Writeup — WebSec Labs</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <p>
      <a href="/" style="color:var(--accent)">← all labs</a>
      &nbsp;·&nbsp;
      <a href="/lab/<%= lab.id %>" style="color:var(--accent)">← <%= lab.title %></a>
    </p>
    <h1>📖 Writeup</h1>
    <p class="tagline"><%= lab.title %></p>
  </header>

  <main>
    <article class="markdown-body"><%- html %></article>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>⚠️ Intentionally vulnerable. Run locally only.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
